loop through question 1 to 5;

Load question 1
Question 1: whole grain or white?
set the counter to 0
if white is selected and submitted, increase the counter to 1;
else log counter to 0;

Display question 2 (???)

Question 2
tomato sauce, pesto, no sauce? (tomato sauce --> counter + 1, else 0)

Question 3
choose cheese from the list (can be more than 1 choice):
cheddar cheese, parmesan cheese, Provolone, mozzarella & gorganzola cheese (cheddar cheese & parmesan cheese --> counter + 1 each, else 0)

Question 4
choose toppings from the provided list:
pepperoni, Italian sausage, fresh green peppers, fresh mushrooms, fresh onions, black olives, tomatoes, smoked bacon, steak slices, baby spinach, roasted red pepper, ground pork, pineapple, chicken strips and ham.
(pepperoni, Italian sausage, fresh green peppers, fresh mushrooms, fresh onions,  + 1 score each, else 0)

Question 5
extra cracked red pepper or garlic powder? (cracked red pepper --> score + 1, else 0)

If getting total 10 points: display "Yay! You won a 14" of our Delux pizza!!!

start again


